title: Microsoft Windows 10 Enterprise (x64) [Tracking Disabled]
description:
This torrent contains an image of a modified Microsoft Windows 10 Enterprise (x64) installation with all tracking features disabled. Further modifications detailed in the link below were made to secure and optimize the operating system. No drivers or updates were installed.

The image was created using the Backup and Restore (Windows 7) feature in Windows 10. An existing copy of Windows 7 or newer must be installed on the computer before completely overwriting it with the image. The installation can be performed using the aforementioned Backup and Restore (Windows 7) utility found in the Control Panel.

We hope you enjoy your newly secured and optimized operating system.
